### medium() → String

Source: lib/src/threshold.dart:7:16

A method with exactly 10 lines body (should be inline at threshold=10).

```dart
String medium() {
  const a = 1;
  const b = 2;
  const c = 3;
  const d = 4;
  const e = 5;
  const f = a + b;
  const g = c + d;
  return '$f$g$e';
}
```

